                                      Working with stored procedures
                                  =============================================


==> Procedure means set of sql queries..
==> procedures are used to write bussiness logic at database side ..
==> Procedures are used to improve performance of the application..


Procedure to retrieve data from product table 


===============================
Sql code to create Procedutre :
===============================

 DELIMITER $$

CREATE PROCEDURE getProducts()
BEGIN
    SELECT
        product_id,
        product_price,
        product_name
    FROM PRODUCT;
END$$

DELIMITER ;
 
 call getProducts();



